; Reproduces the dynamic survex separator bug end to end. Including any Walls
; .srv makes cavern pick ':' (not '.') as the label separator for the whole
; .3d — the exact situation a project with mixed survex + Walls data hits. The
; "*alias station - .." mirrors the external TopoDroid file that surfaced this.
; The nested cave_/trip_ begins mirror the line-plot driver's synthetic
; prefixes, so the emitted labels are the exact form cwCavernNaming decodes.
; The Walls include forces the ':' separator and fixes its own WA station
; (#Fix). The cave below fixes station 1. Both connected components carry a
; control point so cavern emits no warning (the in-process runner surfaces
; warnings as errors).
*include separator_walls.srv

*begin cave_f5881643adce48de9d5fe2224c217a86
*begin trip_6f7da06a8b8c471cbfbefe23b99e4fd4
*begin holberg1
  *units tape meters
  *units compass degrees
  *units clino degrees
  *alias station - ..
  *fix 1 0 0 0
  *data normal from to tape compass clino
    1 2   3.56 221.3 4.5
    1 3   8.21 54.6 -72.6
  1 - 9.25 138.6 85.0
    1 4   9.20 212.0 66.3
    4 5   0.47 257.7 -38.7
*end holberg1
*end trip_6f7da06a8b8c471cbfbefe23b99e4fd4
*end cave_f5881643adce48de9d5fe2224c217a86
